B.FR=s(["Kal aur kharab hoga \u2014 aaj hi ghoom lo.","Kal hawa aur bigdegi. Aaj bahar jaana smart move hai.","Kal ke liye N95 taiyaar rakh lo bhai.","Tomorrow? Downgrade confirmed. Aaj agar nikalna ho toh niklo.","Kal toh andar raho. Aaj ka maza lo."],t.s)
B.H6=s(["Kal thodi saans le paaoge. Kal ka plan banao.","Good news: kal hawa theek hogi. Kal enjoy karo.","Kal better rahega! Aaj indoor, kal outdoor.","Kal thodi rahat milegi. Hold on, wait karo.","Aane wala kal thoda meherbaan lagta hai. Kal niklo."],t.s)
