B.IT=new A.b8(B.JN,["\ud83e\uddb9 Aaj ka villain: PM2.5 \u2014 chhupa rustam, seedha lungs mein ghusega. Mask must.","\ud83d\udca8 Aaj ka villain: PM10 \u2014 dhool ka daitya haazir! Naak aur mooh dhak lo.","\ud83d\ude97 Aaj ka villain: NO2 \u2014 traffic ka kaala tohfa. Sadak se door raho.","\ud83c\udf2b\ufe0f Aaj ka villain: Ozone \u2014 dhoop mein chhupa khatarnak. Dopahar bahar mat jao.","\ud83c\udfed Aaj ka villain: SO2 \u2014 factory ka kaala jaadu. Andar raho yaar.","\ud83d\udd25 Aaj ka villain: CO \u2014 dikhta nahi, par nuksaan karta hai. Hawa aane do.","\ud83c\udf3e Aaj ka villain: Ammonia \u2014 khet se city tak pahuncha. Khidki band karo."],t.l)
